data.description: For more information or showings please contact Danny Umana at 818.571.3261 or Danny@DannyUmana.com Just in time for the summer! Charming curb appeal and located on one of Valley Glen?s most desirable tree lined streets, this lovely, well cared for 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom pool home displays true pride of ownership. Enjoy a spacious living room with plenty of character including a glass fireplace, beautiful hardwood floors and newer dual paned windows with custom shutters that provide incredible natural light. Wall of built-ins, traditional brick fireplace and extra storage closets accent the light and bright den. Formal dining area is enhanced with beautiful sliding glass doors leading to an open entertainers backyard with sparkling swimmers pool, private yard, fruit trees and a detached double garage. Bonus room adjacent to the garage can be used as a storage room or even an office. For more information or showings please contact Danny Umana at 818.571.3261 or Danny@DannyUmana.com Kitchen offers additional eating area and there is an enclosed laundry area with washer and dryer. Price includes all appliances. Newer high efficiency central air and heating system and copper plumbing. Move in Ready!
